@page "/InstructionsKnownTopics"

@inherits InstructionsKnownTopicsPageBase

<MudText>The rule engine subscribes to all topics. All received messages from all topics are displayed in the Mqtt Message Explorer.</MudText>
<br />
<MudText>However, only known topics are relevant for the system.</MudText>
<br />
<MudText>The system remembers the last payload from every known topic, so that it can be called up later again with the function Read("&lt;TopicName&gt").</MudText>

